article.description: — Bryce Hamilton had 22 points and 13 rebounds as UNLV beat Air Force 68-58 on Saturday.
article.headline: Hamilton scores 22 to lift UNLV over Air Force 68-58
article.linkText: Hamilton scores 22 to lift UNLV over Air Force 68-58
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- — Bryce Hamilton had 22 points and 13 rebounds as UNLV beat Air Force 68-58 on Saturday. Cheikh Mbacke Diong had 16 points for UNLV (7-9, 4-5 Mountain West Conference). Nick Blake added 11 points. A.J. Walker had 18 points for the Falcons (4-13, 2-11), whose losing streak stretched to six games. Chris Joyce added 14 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
